{"tid":2339383,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【ViuTV】《膠戰》Be ON Game (3)","createTime":"2020-12-24T14:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T15:33:24.000Z","uid":204077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8266bec523f68a57e09d5a582797d03f393e2421","tid":2339383,"uid":204077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"teal\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">《膠戰》</span></span><br />\n🤡🤡🤡<span class=\"gold\"> Be ON Game </span>🤡🤡🤡</strong><br />\n<span class=\"orange\">12月21日晚起(逢星期一至五) 11點 99台ViuTV</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hn8tLUa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhn8tLUa.jpg&h=e2f3d190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n節目重溫：<a href=\"https://www.viu.tv/encore/be-on-game\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.viu.tv%2Fencore%2Fbe-on-game&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGtxPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=20a4d5d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.viu.tv/encore/be-on-game</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1555649141357168/videos/218457753067233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1555649141357168%2Fvideos%2F218457753067233&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGtxPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=14197e49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1555649141357168/videos/218457753067233</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\">《膠戰》（英語：be ON game）是香港電視娛樂製作的一套遊戲節目，由呂爵安、岑珈其、魏浚笙、徐浩昌、黃正宜及劉沛蘅主持，於2020年12月21日晚起(逢星期一至五)11點在99台ViuTV播出。<br />\n<br />\n六個雜牌兵天生骨骼精奇，各自代表住「弱雞」、「索女」、「靚仔」、「麻甩」、「偶像派」同「肥仔」，大纜都扯唔埋嘅佢哋將會化身派膠專員，進行各種恥力無下限嘅對決，例如「三項膠人賽」、「保護系列」、「口技遊戲」、「一日扮動物」等等，憑住低智商、高技術嘅玩膠行為，為香港人帶嚟歡笑聲！俗語有話，睇人high high最開心！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01QozLM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01QozLM.jpg&h=2b208225&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kUO5N5N.jpg\" data-thumbnai